-- Hitachi to Join 450 Billion Yen Development Project in China, Nikkei Says
-- B y   Y a s u h i k o   S e k i
-- 2010-10-24T00:06:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-24/hitachi-to-join-450-billion-yen-development-project-in-china-nikkei-says.html
Hitachi Ltd. will join a project
worth more than 450 billion yen ($5.5 billion) to develop an
environment-friendly zone in Dalian, China, the Nikkei newspaper
reported, without saying where it got the information.   The project entails the construction of offices, research
institutes, universities and residential areas, the report said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Yasuhiko Seki in Tokyo at 
